## Introduction

A lot of reasons can lead you to start programming with Go:

- You can understand Kubernetes code
- You can build safer software
- You can build system software
- It is open source
- The community is great
- Channels

### Books

- [The Go Programming Language](https://www.oreilly.com/library/view/the-go-programming/9780134190570/): like _The C Programming Language_ from K&R but for Go
